INTALL
======

1.) Unzip.

2.) Upload.

3.) Run the installer, this can be done by navigating to http://www.yoursite.com/installer/index.ph

4.) Remove the installer directory

5.) Set /public_html/config/config.php and /public_html/config/database.php

6.) Permissions.
	
	cd /home/pyrocms/public_html/
	chmod 777 codeigniter/cache
	chmod 777 codeigniter/logs
	chmod -R 777 application/cache
	chmod -R 777 application/uploads
	chmod -R 777 application/assets/img/galleries
	chmod -R 777 application/assets/img/products
	chmod -R 777 application/assets/img/staff
	chmod -R 777 application/assets/img/suppliers

7.) Go to your web root, login as "demo@example.com" with the password "password" and make yourself an admin user account.

8.) Log into your new account and delete demo@example.com.
